stories.title: 1st Final, Carlton Series, Australia v West Indies, Statistical Highlights
stories.summary: It was the 1685th ODI in cricket history

stories.title: And defeat goes on
stories.summary: Sydney: The West Indies made runs harder to come by but still presented cheap wickets as Australia trounced them in the first of the best-of-three finals in the Carlton Series at the SCG last night

stories.title: Finality comes early to opening Carlton Series final
stories.summary:
If finals are deigned to be more exciting, more tense and more competitive affairs than most of the games which precede them, then today's opening bout of the
Carlton Series deciders between Australia and West Indies didn't necessarily fail the test

recentReportStory.title: Finality comes early to opening Carlton Series final
recentReportStory.summary:
If finals are deigned to be more exciting, more tense and more competitive affairs than most of the games which precede them, then today's opening bout of the
Carlton Series deciders between Australia and West Indies didn't necessarily fail the test
